<tr bgcolor="#9999cc"><td valign="bottom" class="clsSmall">&nbsp;<i>Kocho Divah</i></td><td valign="bottom" align="right" class="clsSmall">&nbsp;&nbsp;Monday, February 11, 2002&nbsp;&nbsp;6:27pm CST</b></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="2" bgcolor="#eeeeee"><br><blockquote>I got a call from the webhosting company stating I was 200mb over my storage limit. No biggie, I'm deleting a bunch of stuff, mostly the Screenshots, which has been disabled for months now anyway.<br><br>While I'm doing this, I'm placing a Website Freeze on EQDiva to temporarily halt any new Hunting Guides, Song Comments, etc... coming in. Over the next month I'll be upgrading the site to SQL Server 2000 and C#.<br><br>I'm also currently inactive in EQ again, so its less responsibility for me to review all the Song Comments and such.</blockquote></td></tr>
